snippet.title: Diana Pretends to be a Nanny for Baby Oliver
snippet.description:
Diana puts baby Oliver to bed and falls asleep herself. Waking up, the girl sees that her little brother is missing. Diana is looking for baby Oliver, but only finds dolls. Where has the baby gone? Watch this funny video for kids from Diana and Roma.
